Title: It's a Fae, Fae, Fae, Fae World
Plot: Bo has been living on the run from her strange appetites and what havoc they wreak. After leaving someone she kills out in the open, she is contacted by a group called The Fae. She discovers who and what she is, and is told to join one of two tribes.
ParentalRatingReason: Contains violence, horror and sex scenes
